37:06.125 --> 37:09.667
Woman over P.A.: <i>GOOD MORNING,</i>
<i>OCEAN PARK STAFFERS.</i>

37:09.750 --> 37:11.000
<i>PLEASE REPORT TO</i>
<i>CONFERENCE ROOM E-35</i>
<i>FOR THE MORNING MEETING.</i>

37:11.083 --> 37:12.834
JACKSON. HEY.

37:12.917 --> 37:14.583
CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A SECOND?

37:14.667 --> 37:16.291
ACTUALLY,
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU.

37:16.375 --> 37:19.667
I, UH,
WANTED TO APOLOGIZE.

37:19.750 --> 37:22.250
I WAS WRONG ABOUT EVA.

37:23.375 --> 37:24.667
DON'T GIVE ME THAT LOOK.

37:24.750 --> 37:26.291
YES,
EVEN I MAKE MISTAKES.

37:26.375 --> 37:28.125
NOT THIS TIME.

37:28.208 --> 37:30.500
EVA LEFT LAST NIGHT.

37:30.583 --> 37:31.875
WHAT'S THIS?

37:31.959 --> 37:34.083
SHE IS RELINQUISHING
GUARDIANSHIP OF JORDI.

37:34.166 --> 37:35.583
HE'S OFFICIALLY ON HIS WAY

37:35.667 --> 37:37.875
TO BECOMING
AN EMANCIPATED MINOR.

37:37.959 --> 37:40.375
WHICH IS JUST A FANCY WORD
FOR ALONE.

37:40.458 --> 37:44.000
SO, I'M THE ONE WHO NEEDS
TO APOLOGIZE TO YOU.

37:44.083 --> 37:47.333
I'M SORRY FOR NOT TRUSTING
YOUR INSTINCTS.

37:47.417 --> 37:51.083
WE BOTH WANT THE SAME THING --
WHAT'S BEST FOR JORDI.

37:51.166 --> 37:52.375
I GUESS HE'S OURS NOW.

37:52.458 --> 37:54.000
[ SCOFFS ]

37:54.083 --> 37:55.959
HE WAS OURS THE SECOND HE WALKED
THROUGH THAT DOOR.

37:58.291 --> 38:00.750
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

38:00.834 --> 38:04.208
I HAVE THE 4-1-1

38:04.291 --> 38:06.625
ON WHAT HAPPENED
AFTER YOU LEFT HOMECOMING.

38:06.709 --> 38:07.834
DON'T CARE.

38:07.917 --> 38:09.291
OKAY.

38:09.375 --> 38:10.834
WELL, I ALSO HAVE THE 4-1-1
ON ANNA'S PROGRESS

38:10.917 --> 38:12.250
AFTER YOUR WHEELCHAIR
CRUSHED HER.

38:12.333 --> 38:13.834
DON'T CARE.

38:13.917 --> 38:16.875
I DON'T CARE ABOUT
THE CROOKED GIRL OR HOMECOMING

38:16.959 --> 38:18.417
OR PARADISE COVE HIGH.

38:18.500 --> 38:20.333
I'M NEVER GOING BACK THERE.

38:22.625 --> 38:25.667
WAIT. REALLY?

38:25.750 --> 38:27.417
REALLY.

38:29.333 --> 38:32.583
YOU ARE OFFICIALLY RELIEVED
OF YOUR DUTIES AS MINION.

38:37.583 --> 38:39.709
WELL,
CAN I STILL COME VISIT YOU,

38:39.792 --> 38:41.500
LIKE,
JUST AS YOUR FRIEND?

38:41.583 --> 38:44.959
IT'S A FREE COUNTRY,
SO DO WHATEVER YOU WANT.

38:47.583 --> 38:49.667
[ MID-TEMPO GUITAR MUSIC PLAYS ]

39:08.375 --> 39:10.083
I DON'T WANT TI
TO TRAIN ME.

39:10.166 --> 39:12.834
IF NEXT WEEK ISN'T GOOD,
WE CAN TRY FOR THE WEEK AFTER.

39:12.917 --> 39:13.959
I'LL GIVE HIM A CALL.

39:14.041 --> 39:15.333
NO, YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

39:15.417 --> 39:16.834
I DON'T WANT TI
TO TRAIN ME EVER.

39:16.917 --> 39:19.000
HOW ARE YOU GONNA GET
THAT SCHOLARSHIP?

39:19.083 --> 39:20.625
I'M NOT.

39:20.709 --> 39:24.834
I DID A LITTLE MORE RESEARCH,
AND EVERY ARTICLE ON TI

39:24.917 --> 39:27.000
STARTS WITH THE INCREDIBLE STORY
OF HIS DISEASE.

39:27.083 --> 39:29.875
THAT'S BECAUSE HE'S MADE
A REMARKABLE RECOVERY.

39:29.959 --> 39:32.583
HE BEAT IMPOSSIBLE ODDS,
JUST LIKE YOU WILL.

39:32.667 --> 39:35.542
I'M NOT GONNA BE THE SOCCER
PLAYER WHO SURVIVED CANCER --

39:35.625 --> 39:37.750
YOU KNOW, THE GUY THEY PARADE
OUT AT HALF TIME

39:37.834 --> 39:43.000
LIKE SOME FUZZY MASCOT AND GIVES
INSPIRATIONAL SPEECHES...

39:43.083 --> 39:45.792
'CAUSE I'M NOT
A SOB STORY.

39:45.875 --> 39:50.000
I JUST WANT TO BE
A REGULAR GUY.

40:09.625 --> 40:12.083
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

40:18.709 --> 40:20.333
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:34.542 --> 40:36.417
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

40:36.500 --> 40:40.000
[ IAN COTTERILL'S
"LOOKING TO THE SEA" PLAYS ]

