<i>I'VE BEEN THINKING A LOT ABOUT</i>
<i>THIS CONCEPT OF HOME.</i>

40:45.083 --> 40:48.208
♪ IN THE MORNING
WITH THE SUNRISE ♪

40:48.291 --> 40:49.959
♪ WHEN THE LIGHT BEGS
TO OPEN UP YOUR EYES ♪

40:50.041 --> 40:53.583
<i>HOME DOESN'T HAVE TO BE</i>
<i>WHO YOU ONCE WERE...</i>

40:55.917 --> 40:57.709
