40:57.792 --> 41:01.542
♪ THERE'S A CHANCE
TO MAKE IT ALL NEW ♪

41:01.625 --> 41:05.041
♪ START AGAIN
AND GIVE IT ANOTHER TRY ♪

41:05.125 --> 41:07.250
<i>...OR WHAT YOU DID</i>
<i>OR WHERE YOU WERE FROM.</i>

41:10.667 --> 41:13.875
♪ WHAT ARE YOU LEAVING? ♪

41:13.959 --> 41:16.375
♪ WHAT ARE YOU MISSING? ♪

41:16.458 --> 41:18.208
<i>HOME JUST MIGHT BE</i>
<i>THE FEELING YOU GET</i>

41:18.291 --> 41:20.834
<i>AROUND THE PEOPLE</i>
<i>THAT CARE ABOUT YOU THE MOST.</i>

41:20.917 --> 41:25.083
♪ ARE YOU LIVING? ♪

41:25.166 --> 41:29.417
<i>AND IF THAT'S THE CASE,</i>
<i>YOU MIGHT ALREADY BE HOME.</i>
